{"tid":1676490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯漢：執法者須在權限内　以良知執法守法　","createTime":"2019-10-26T13:19:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T16:54:15.000Z","uid":77416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"14025ef03bb30a94a3c9ad71542abd42f40ee315","tid":1676490,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:19:26.000Z","msg":"想睇下廢老kol同班散仔級點回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n天主教香港教區宗座署理湯漢樞機接受《梵蒂岡新聞網》的專訪，回應香港連月反送中運動。他呼籲香港市民懷著希望及避免暴力，亦要求執法者必須在其權限内以良知執法和守法，以重建民衆對他們的信任和尊敬。<br />\n<br />\n望民衆不要絕望<br />\n<br />\n湯漢在訪問中提出呼籲民衆不要喪失希望，指在合理的訴求無法獲得接納時，希望民衆不要絕望，「因為絕望讓人無法看到未來，它會耗盡我們的生命」。他又指以暴易暴不能解決眼前問題，只會招來更大的危機和傷害。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B9%AF%E6%BC%A2-%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E8%80%85%E9%A0%88%E5%9C%A8%E6%AC%8A%E9%99%90%E5%86%85-%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%AF%E7%9F%A5%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%88%E6%B3%95-%E4%BB%A5%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB/?fbclid=IwAR1I5rOkwqcPEZJCQ2YUUHVg5bDM982FjxUUlD__iegYMyEGg2hmllPzQ14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E6%25BC%25A2-%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%25A0%2588%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25AC%258A%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%2586%2585-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2589%25AF%25E7%259F%25A5%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2588%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25BB%25BB%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1I5rOkwqcPEZJCQ2YUUHVg5bDM982FjxUUlD__iegYMyEGg2hmllPzQ14&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=491a6a9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E6%25BC%25A2-%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%25A0%2588%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25AC%258A%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%2586%2585-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2589%25AF%25E7%259F%25A5%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2588%25E6%25B3%2595-%25