得真係好撚on9</span></span><br />\n推今晚集會post 又唔見你咁勤力？<br />\n推聽日尖沙咀集會又唔見你會咁勤力？<br />\n一間咁嘅濕鳩食肆，一間咁大間嘅食肆唔通奶共會唔知咩<br />\n洗唔洗幾百個post 一齊討論呀屌<br />\n<br />\n爭氣d 啦，唔好犀比班濕鳩五毛睇<br />\n多啲獨立思考，拒絕風向<br />\n光復香港唔係靠熱血就夠，仲要智慧架大佬<br />\n一齊努力，要班五毛無糧出"},{"pid":"a970a72c31a86a802ccb981603eeb9f50de430fc","tid":1676490,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6ba0e9d70918ab18ceaffba99b6e1dfc90df055","tid":1676490,"uid":163931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:21:10.000Z","msg":"四個協會要準備發聲明了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:34:31.000Z","msg":"佢地又唔做野 又唔讀書 大把時間寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3fd18fbf0ce15e8d4dde9843702aeff96fed75","tid":1676490,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:35:26.000Z","msg":"湯漢毛漢"},{"pid":"5bb0144819418ecb3f111f98957fb1d98c72f13e","tid":1676490,"uid":326414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c917741b49545c5dc5074c7c72fe40c581df7c24","tid":1676490,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bb0144819418ecb3f111f98957fb1d98c72f13e","tid":1676490,"uid":326414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:54:15.000Z","msg":"推到cy同班散仔回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班人咁撚鐘意狙擊<br />\n俾佢地順便狙埋天主教樞機<br />\nDklm"}]}